# OR
# --- Jellyfin ----------------------------------------------
# Pick Option A OR Option B below, not both.
#
# Option A: Real-time (recommended)
#   Jellyfin sends PlaybackProgress webhooks continuously as you watch.
#   Episeerr fires once when progress lands in the MIN-MAX window.
#   Webhook URL to configure in Jellyfin: http://<episeerr>:5002/jellyfin-webhook
#   Notification type: PlaybackProgress
#
# Option B: Polling
#   Jellyfin sends a playback.start webhook, then Episeerr polls
#   Jellyfin's /Sessions API every POLL_INTERVAL seconds until the
#   TRIGGER_PERCENTAGE is reached.
#   Webhook URL to configure in Jellyfin: http://<episeerr>:5002/jellyfin-webhook
#   Notification type: PlaybackStart
#
# JELLYFIN_URL=http://your-jellyfin:8096
# JELLYFIN_API_KEY=your_jellyfin_api_key
# JELLYFIN_USER_ID=your_username
#
# Option A vars:
# JELLYFIN_TRIGGER_MIN=50.0
# JELLYFIN_TRIGGER_MAX=55.0
#
# Option B vars:
# JELLYFIN_TRIGGER_PERCENTAGE=50.0
# JELLYFIN_POLL_INTERVAL=900

# --- Emby --------------------------------------------------
# Emby sends playback.start/stop webhooks. Episeerr polls Emby's
# /Sessions API in the background until TRIGGER_PERCENTAGE is reached,
# so the next episode starts downloading while you're still watching.
# Webhook URL to configure in Emby:
#   User Preferences -> Notifications -> Add Notification -> Webhooks
#   URL: http://<episeerr>:5002/emby-webhook
#   Events: playback.start, playback.stop
#
## - EMBY_TRIGGER_PERCENTAGE and EMBY_POLL_INTERVAL will fall back
##   to their JELLYFIN_ counterparts if not explicitly set here.
      
# Optional - Request integration
JELLYSEERR_URL=http://your-jellyseerr:5055
JELLYSEERR_API_KEY=your_jellyseerr_key
# OR  
OVERSEERR_URL=http://your-overseerr:5055
OVERSEERR_API_KEY=your_overseerr_key
      





